Release 1.2
===========

- Dropped support for PostgreSQL before 8.3 and for Snowball lexer.
- Installation Makefile uses PGXS to install files in the right place.
- Added extension metadata for PG 9.1 and uninstall script.


Release 1.1 (released 2007-07-09)
=================================

- Added installation script for PostgreSQL 8.3.
- Package released in utf8 and latin1 encoding.
- Added Snowball lexer.


Version 1.0 (released 2007-06-28)
=================================

- Initial release: for PostgreSQL up to 8.2.
